Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:13.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}We erase it from our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:20.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}You can't escape I only know this secret with you
