Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Inside of Kaos I say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:18.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Where can I get the real love and fate, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:21.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}How can I make you know my heart is with you hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:28.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}人間は誰も忘れていく痛めた傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:35.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}時の流れ見送る度に薄れる感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:40.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}たけどこれ以上見過ごしたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:41.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Back and forth　心中叫んでやまない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:45.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}time over　消えていく残像それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:50.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたそのものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:50.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So now that you & I
